#### S#4 (06s~08s)

**Visual Description:** 여성의 옆 얼굴 실루엣. 얼굴 위로 빛과 그림자의 날카로운 대비가 움직이며, 피부의 질감과 윤곽선을 마치 조각처럼 섬세하게 드러낸다.
```json
{
 "prompt": "A sleek, minimalist glass dropper bottle with a golden cap, holding a shimmering amber serum, A pristine, futuristic gallery space with geometric patterns and cool lighting, Elegant Korean woman in her late 30s, radiant skin, sophisticated aura, Medium shot of woman's profile, sharp, high-contrast light and shadow playing across her face, accentuating her refined features and skin texture like a sculpted masterpiece, Hard/High Contrast lighting, Hasselblad X2D, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "sculptural, dramatic", "color": "monochromatic, sharp highlights", "lighting": "directional, impactful" }
}
```
