 "prompt": "A sleek, minimalist glass dropper bottle with a golden cap, holding a shimmering amber serum, A bright, airy penthouse apartment overlooking a vibrant city skyline, Elegant Korean woman in her late 30s, radiant skin, sophisticated aura, Long shot of the woman standing by a large panoramic window overlooking a vibrant city skyline, smiling radiantly, embodying confidence and elegance, High-Key lighting, ARRI Alexa, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "empowering, triumphant", "color": "vibrant, elegant", "lighting": "clear, expansive" }
}
```
```json
{
 "prompt": "A sweeping steadycam shot reveals the woman, now radiant and poised, standing confidently against the stunning backdrop of the city, truly transformed."
}
```
